WASHINGTON DC — Amalunga enhlanganiso yeWomen of Zimbabwe Arise (WOZA) edlula amakhulu amabili atshengisele eHarare ngoLwesibili ekhonona ngodaba lwesisekelo sombuso esitsha. Ukutshengisela lokhu kulandele okwangoMvulo koBulawayo lapho amalunga alinhlanganiso angene ezitaladeni ekhonona ngodaba lunye. IWoza yinhlanganiso ekhankasela ukulondolozwa kwamalungelo abesifazana njalo ihlezi itshengisela phezu kwezinto ezitshiyeneyo. Inhlanganiso le ithi ifuna uhulumende abize umhlangano weSecond All-Stakeholders Conference kuhlaziywe isisekelo sombuso. Isiphathamandla seWoza, uNkosazana Magodonga Mahlangu utshele iStudio 7 ukuthi njengakoBulawayo, akulamuntu obotshiweyo ekutshengiseleni kwabo eHarare.

INgilandi INgilandi (isiNgisi: England) izwe laseYurophu. Isiqongo saseNgilandi iLondon. Ulimi isiNgisi. INgilandi yizwe eliyingxenye yOmbuso Ohlangeneyo. Lingumakhelwane nesiKotilandi enyakatho kanjalo neWelisi entshonalanga; Ulwandle lwase-Ayilendi luse nyakatho-ntshonalanga, Ulwandle lwaseKeltiki luseningizimu-ntshonalanga kanti Ulwandle lwaseNyakatho lusempumalanga, Insungubezi yamaNgisi eningizimu ihlukanisa iNgilandi kwizwekazi laseYurophu(continental Europe). Ingxenye enkulu yeNgilandi yakhiwe yingxenye emaphakathi nengxenye eseningizimu ye-island (izwe elincane elizungezwe amanzi ngokuphelele) yaseBrithani Enkulu(Great Britain) e-Atlantic eseNyakatho. INgilandi ihlanganisa futhi amazwe amancane azungezwe amazi ngokuphelele angaphezu kwekhulu njenge-ziqhingi Scilly ne-siqhingi Wight.

'Umsebenzi omkhulu' ukuvula iphalamande: Zuma 2011-02-10 07:42 Johannesburg - UMengameli wakuleli uJacob Zuma ukuthatha njengomsebenzi obalulekile ukwethula inkulumo ebhekiswe esizweni, esho emsakazweni mayelana nokuvulwa kwePhalamende ngoLwesine. "Uvuka nje, uyazi ukuthi unomsebenzi omkhulu emahlombe akho," kusho uZuma ekhuluma emsakazweni iSAfm ngoLwesine ekuseni. "Isizwe yisona esikubeka la kanti futhi silindele ukuzwa usibikela ukuthi ubuwenzani, uphinde usho nokuthi usazosenzelani ngemisebenzi oyibona phambi kwamehlo akho. "Ngakho ke, uyazilungiselela ukuthi ngizobe ngikhuluma nesizwe -- nokuyinkulumo ebaluleke kunazo zonke," kusho uZuma. Ube esethola izingcingo eziqhamuka kubantu bakuleli ezimcela ukuthi enkulumweni yakhe athinte ubugebengu, inkohlakalo nemfundo. - SAPA
